metadata.name: Vaporwave Starry Night - 1st Edition
metadata.description:
This is an original piece of AI generated art created by DALL路E 2.

DALL路E 2 is an AI system that can create realistic images & art from a description in natural language.

DALL路E 2 helps us understand how advanced AI systems see & understand our world, which is critical to our mission of creating AI that benefits humanity.

This NFT is a 3D object that can be imported to metaverse applications like Spatial as well as other compatible applications.

10% of profits made from sales of this NFT go to PhygiEd programs. PhygiEd workshops and educational resources are aimed at providing diverse audiences equitable opportunities in Web3 & the metaverse.
